 4%。特斯拉一季度营收 233.29 亿美元，自由现金流降至两年最低！盘后一度跌超 4%，马斯克最新发声... | 每经网"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-d31b3370a768ed695653c3567b0ff068_720w.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/596667429"}}, "attached_info": "ClUI/dyBvMrkx9BPEAMaCDk0ODczNjkxIPGSgqIGMAk4uAJALHIJNTk2NjY3NDI5eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQDyARMIARIPZG9tYWluX29wZXJhdG9y"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "45_1682044030.6760967", "card_id": "Q_596682673", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 84}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "要考驾照了，科目一有什么口诀和技巧吗?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-31a723daac1de77f755ef79e3966c98c_1440w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/596682673"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I/dyBvMrkx9BPEAMaCDk0ODc3MDk4IOXIgqIGMAI4/wFALXIJNTk2NjgyNjczeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "46_1682044030.6768095", "card_id": "Q_596686682", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 190}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价折叠屏当前的技术积累，厂商在科技探索和实用体验的平衡上都做了哪些努力？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "随着折叠屏市场热度日益高涨，厂商们加大了折叠屏的研发投入力度，以今日发布的 vivo X Fold2 和 vivo X Flip 为例，折叠屏有哪些新奇体验让消费者心甘情愿买单？在科技发展和使用体验之间，厂商又该如何把握这个平衡点？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-5172680b2bbd0c4595d4f42aa182e945_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "6 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/596686682"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I/dyBvMrkx9BPEAMaCDk0ODc3OTkw